    <div class="grain"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>38 Headline Techniques</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">The Eugene Schwartz Verbalization Framework</p>
        </header>

        <div class="intro-card">
            <h2>What is Verbalization?</h2>
            <p>Eugene Schwartz defined verbalization as the art of increasing the impact of a headline by the way it is stated. Once you determine the content of your headline (the basic appeal), verbalization shows you how to say it to maximize its force. This workbook helps you apply all 38 techniques to strengthen any headline you're working on.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- CATEGORY 1: INTENSIFYING THE CLAIM -->
        <div class="category-section">
            <div class="category-header">
                <div class="category-number">01</div>
                <h2 class="category-title">Intensifying the Claim</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="techniques-grid">
                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="1">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#01</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Measure the Size of the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use specific numbers to provide scale and make your claim tangible.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "20,000 filter traps in Viceroy"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="Try adding a specific number to quantify your benefit..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="2">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#02</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Measure the Speed of the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Highlight how quickly the product works to create urgency and appeal.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Feel better fast" / "Results in 7 days"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="How fast does your product deliver results?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="3">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#03</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Compare the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use a comparative standard to show superiority over alternatives.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Six times whiter washes"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What can you compare your product to?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="4">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#04</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Metaphorize the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use strong verbs to create a vivid mental image of action.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Melt away ugly fat" / "Blast through barriers"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What powerful verb captures your benefit?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="5">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#05</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Sensitize the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Make the prospect feel, smell, touch, see, or hear the benefit.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "The skin you love to touch"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="Which sense can you activate?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="6">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#06</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Demonstrate with a Prime Example</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Show the product succeeding in a difficult or extreme situation.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> Fighter fails to flatten a paper cup (strength demonstration)
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What extreme test could your product pass?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="7">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#07</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Dramatize the Claim or Result</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use a narrative hook to show the dramatic outcome.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "They laughed when I sat down at the piano..."
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What's the dramatic before-and-after story?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CATEGORY 2: MODIFYING THE CLAIM'S LOGIC -->
        <div class="category-section">
            <div class="category-header">
                <div class="category-number">02</div>
                <h2 class="category-title">Modifying the Claim's Logic</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="techniques-grid">
                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="8">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#08</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">State as a Paradox</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Create intrigue through apparent contradiction.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "How a bald-headed barber saved my hair"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What contradiction makes your claim intriguing?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="9">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#09</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Remove Limitations</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Promise a result without the usual drawbacks.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Shrinks hemorrhoids without surgery"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What painful step does your solution eliminate?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="10">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#10</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Associate with Values or People</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Connect the product to figures the prospect admires.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Mickey Mantle says: Camels never bother my throat"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="Who does your audience admire or trust?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="11">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#11</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Show Work Done in Detail</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">List specific problems solved to demonstrate comprehensive value.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Relief from all 5 acid-caused stomach troubles"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="List the specific problems your product solves..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="12">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#12</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">State as a Question</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Engage the reader directly with a compelling question.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Who else wants a whiter wash—with no hard work?"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What question would make your reader say 'me!'?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="13">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#13</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Offer Information About How</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Frame the headline as a guide or instructional promise.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "How to win friends and influence people"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="How to [achieve desired outcome]..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="14">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#14</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Tie Authority Into the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use an expert figure to back the promise.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Here's what doctors do when they feel rotten"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What authority figure validates your claim?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="15">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#15</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Before-and-After the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Contrast the state before and after product use.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "From broke to $10k/month in 90 days"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What's the transformation your product creates?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CATEGORY 3: NEWNESS, EXCLUSIVITY & CHALLENGES -->
        <div class="category-section">
            <div class="category-header">
                <div class="category-number">03</div>
                <h2 class="category-title">Newness, Exclusivity & Challenges</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="techniques-grid">
                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="16">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#16</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Stress the Newness</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use words like "Announcing" or "Now" to signal a breakthrough.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Announcing: The first wrinkle cream that actually works"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What's new or breakthrough about your offer?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="17">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#17</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Stress the Exclusivity</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Highlight what "only" your product can do.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Ours alone!" / "The only system that..."
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What can only your product deliver?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="18">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#18</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Turn Into a Challenge</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Ask a question that forces the reader to compare.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Which twin has the Toni?"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What comparison challenge can you create?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="19">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#19</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Case-History Quotation</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Use a "real" voice from an actual user or customer.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Look, Mom—no cavities!"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What would a satisfied customer say?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="20">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#20</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Condense the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Interchange the product with the thing it replaces.</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "A ring and piston job in a tube"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What does your product replace or compress?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="technique-card" data-technique="21">
                    <div class="technique-header">
                        <span class="technique-num">#21</span>
                        <h3 class="technique-name">Symbolize the Claim</h3>
                    </div>
                    <p class="technique-description">Replace a direct measurement with a "parallel reality."</p>
                    <div class="technique-example">
                        <strong>Example:</strong> "Makes the Atlantic Ocean one-fifth as long"
                    </div>
                    <div class="worksheet-area">
                        <label class="worksheet-label">Your Headline:</label>
                        <textarea class="input-field" placeholder="What vivid metaphor captures your benefit?"></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CATEGORY 4: MECHANISM & INFORMATION -->
        <div class="category-section">
